Here is the patch i use to allow ruby to open abstract sockets.

Install method:

apt-get build-dep ruby1.8
apt-get source ruby1.8
cp 903_abstract_unix_socket.patch ruby1.8-1.8.5/debian/patches/
cd ruby1.8-1.8.5
dpkg-buildpackage -uc -us -rfakeroot
dpkg -i ../libruby1.8*.deb

The patch is certainly unclean but it works for dbus.

